catalogservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"多个服务调用productcatalogservice时出现'connection refused'错误（状态码14），连接目标IP 10.233.54.177:3550被拒绝，表明productcatalogservice完全不可用\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"前端服务出现大量HTTP 500错误（状态码13），正常调用耗时从11.3秒降至242毫秒，表明发生Fast Fail熔断，延迟倍数0.02（242ms/11.3s）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"下单服务PlaceOrder操作正常耗时145秒，异常时降至45秒，延迟倍数0.31，表明下单流程因依赖服务不可用而快速失败\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现分析\n\n**根因定位**: `productcatalogservice` 是明确的根因服务，表现为：\n- 多个上游服务（frontend、recommendationservice、checkoutservice）调用时均出现\"connection refused\"错误\n- 目标地址 `10.233.54.177:3550` 完全无法连接\n- 这是调用链中最下游的服务故障\n\n**错误传播路径**:\n1. `productcatalogservice` 完全不可用（连接被拒绝）\n2. `frontend` 因依赖服务不可用而返回HTTP 500错误\n3. `recommendationservice` 推荐功能受到影响\n4. `checkoutservice` 下单功能部分失败\n\n**延迟特征**: 异常时响应时间大幅下降（从秒级降至毫秒级），这是典型的Fast Fail模式，表明系统检测到下游服务不可用后快速返回错误，而不是等待超时。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "11f619f0-285", "component": "productcatalogservice", "reason": "port misconfiguration causing connection refused at 10.233.54.177:3550 and rrt_max spike", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LoadMetrics(productcatalogservice)", "observation": "productcatalogservice-2 error_ratio p99 increased from 0.0 to 6.44, client_error_ratio anomaly detected"}, {"step": 2, "action": "LogSearch(front